The fish tacos + flavored lemonades are AWESOME.
The fish tacos are grilled + creamy, not fried or crunchy.
The list of flavors for the lemonade are ENDLESS (think beyond your basic berries, they've got prickly pear, mango, even blood orange!
)  I've also had the chicken burrito and i wasn't really feeling it.
Both the rice + beans in the burro were undercooked and ended up just being hard little rocks.
I'd rec this place if you're looking for bombass lemonade, not chicken burritos.

